"The Ukraine" is NOT correct. It is not the proper name of the country. The official United States Government styling is "Ukraine." "The Ukraine" is not acceptable.

Removed "the Ukraine" at the top of the article. Addition of "the" is an obsolete Soviet-era construct and is incorrect. The official United States Government and United Nations renderings are simply "Ukraine" or "Republic of Ukraine" without the preceding "the" article. Please do not revert this to the previous style, as it is offensive to Ukrainians and incorrect.
